snippet.title: Burger Witch Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Store: cyber752.itch.io/burgerwitch

🧙 Welcome Witches! Your time has come to use your witchcraft to bring the most delicious burgers ever! Enjoy the most delicious spooky experience.

A witch that cooks burgers in her dungeon, in a spooky flavored burger-making experience. Enjoy the thrill with your friends as all of you try to complete orders before it's too late.

V1.0 is now out on Itch.io 
Up to four players making burgers together.

Credits:

Creator of this Madness
Programming, Game Design,
Video editing and graphic Designing:
Andrew Mikhail (Cyber752)

Models:
@KayKit @L2S ARTS
@CodeMonkeyUnity
@Oliver Addison @Kenney
@MaxParata @Openlab
Boombox by Poly by Google [CC-BY]
(creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/)
via Poly Pizza
(poly.pizza/m/4hZk7Fg8KiP)

Textures: @Camisado Studios

UI elements:
@Prompts by Mr. Breakfast
@helloerika
Shop Image by upklyak on Freepik.
Flat pattern design
for Halloween season
celebration Image by Freepik.

Font:
Poppins by
@Indian Type Foundry, Jonny Pinhorn

Music:
Coma-Media from Pixabay
DayFox from Pixabay
yourtunes from Pixabay
Onoychenkomusic from Pixabay
Yurii Semchyshyn from Pixabay
AlexiAction from Pixabay
geoffharvey from Pixabay
Dmitry Taras from Pixabay

SFX:
@CodeMonkeyUnity
@Pixabay @JDSherbert
@AlesiaDavina from Pixabay

Special Thanks:

Thanks to my Mum, Family, and Friends.
